latestPosts.caption:
Dreams don’t come true unless you are willing to put in the work and hustle!
During the prop round of Mrs Universe USA, I had faced the challenge of making my prop (which was technically difficult to put together), in a small area… yes, I used the bathroom floor! I knew that I had to stay focused and be willing to put in the work! “I got this” I said to myself and was able to carry it with confidence on the stage. 
I have had several women who have reached out to me following being  crowned as Mrs Universe USA elite 2rup and said that my prop was inspiring to them! To me, that is success!!! 

Stay tuned for more on my prop story 🤗

Credits/ Shoutouts & Special thanks:
🌸CEO/Founder of My DreamMrs Universe USA @mydreamtvusa @janakbedi_official  @rashmibedi_official  and @suryabedi_official. I cannot thank you all for this amazing opportunity and I have to give a SPECIAL SHOUT OUT to them for being so patient, kind, and fair to all. You are appreciated from the bottom of my ❤️

🎬👠Show Director, Coach & Choreographer Mrs Universe USA/WFW show @meenaldrockz  @DrockzCoaching by @CoachDrockz @Meenaldrockz… Meenal you are an INCREDIBLY talented coach and I feel so lucky to be coached by you! Hugs 🤗 

💃Talent Director Mrs UNIVERSE USA/WFW show @ruhaish  @kailashmandal… you made this journey so smooth … you are a ROCKSTAR! 💪🏼 

MUA 💄 @imshakibamoradi Shakiba you are an AMAZING makeup artist, just WOW!  I have to also tell the world that you are so sweet and a beautiful person inside out 😘 

Picture credit @prabug_photography and @m_k_photography26 … thank you both for the AMAZING captures 📸

This Mother’s Day, take a moment to celebrate you.
Celebrate the strength you show, the love you give, the dreams you carry, and the battles you’ve quietly won.
You are more powerful, more beautiful, and more extraordinary than words could ever capture.
Today isn’t just about being appreciated — it’s about appreciating yourself.
You deserve to be honored, loved, and celebrated — not just today, but every day.
Happy Mother’s Day to all the incredible women writing their own stories of courage, love, and endless grace.

latestPosts.caption:
There is a fire inside you — unbreakable, and alive.
It speaks in the quiet moments and roars when you dare to dream.
Listen to it.

You were not born to play small, to hide behind fear, or to wait for permission.
You were born to rise — bold, brilliant, and limitless.
The dreams in your heart are not accidents; they are the whispers of your destiny calling you forward.

Break the barriers that tell you ‘you can’t.’
Shatter the ceilings that try to contain your light.
Stand tall in a world that may not always be ready for your power — and shine anyway.

Each bold step you take plants hope in the heart of someone else.
Each wall you tear down clears the path for others to follow.

Be the revolution wrapped in grace.
Be the storm wrapped in purpose.
Be everything you were told you could never be — and more.

This is your time.
Dream louder. Live braver. Love wilder.
The world has been waiting for! ❤️
